snippet: The Marvel cinematic universe is expanding with new characters Doctor Strange, Black Panther and Captain Marvel, who will be the first female superhero to anchor her own Marvel film, the Walt Disney Co-owned studio said on Tuesday....

headline.print_headline: Marvel Expands With Dr. Strange, Female Captain Marvel Films
headline.main: Marvel Expands With Dr. Strange, Female Captain Marvel Films

lead_paragraph: The Marvel cinematic universe is expanding with new characters Doctor Strange, Black Panther and Captain Marvel, who will be the first female superhero to anchor her own Marvel film, the Walt Disney Co-owned studio said on Tuesday.
